    <item>
      <title>比特币从 10 万美元回落，创特朗普胜选以来最差纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/bitcoin-btc-retreats-from-100-000-in-worst-spell-since-trump-s-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币创下了唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国大选以来最长的连续下跌记录，一度跌至 10 万美元，冷却了由候任总统对加密货币的拥抱所引发的投机狂热。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/bitcoin-btc-retreats-from-100-000-in-worst-spell-since-trump-s-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 01:13:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普加密货币项目获 Sun 3000 万美元投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/trump-crypto-project-gets-30-million-investment-from-justin-sun</link>
      <description><![CDATA[备受争议的中国出生的加密货币企业家孙宇晨向当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的世界自由金融 (World Liberty Financial) 投资了 3000 万美元，成为该去中心化金融项目的最大投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/trump-crypto-project-gets-30-million-investment-from-justin-sun</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 20:14:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币涨势在接近历史性 10 万美元水平后停滞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/bitcoin-s-btc-rally-stalls-after-nearing-the-historic-100-000-level</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币一度上涨至 10 万美元，但在接近历史水平后回落，随后趋于稳定，交易员正在评估当选总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 对加密货币的支持所带来的乐观情绪是否变得过分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/bitcoin-s-btc-rally-stalls-after-nearing-the-historic-100-000-level</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 22:00:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
